# Competitive Analysis

## Competitors

### Jobright AI 
Strengths: AI job matching, resume tailoring, career copilot   Weakness: Limited focus on learning and long-term career growth

### Teal        
Strengths: Job tracking, keyword matching, resume management   Weakness: Productivity-focused rather than coaching            

### Simplify    
Strengths: One-click applications, autofill, AI resume builder Weakness: Optimized for speed, limited decision support  

### Enhancv    
Strengths: Resume builder, ATS optimization                    Weakness: Resume-centric, limited end-to-end career guidance  

